messages.content: Please welcome the Participant and make a short introduction to the experiment. Then, ask if the Participant is ready to begin. After that, proceed with the Experiment whenever asked to speak.
messages.name: chat_manager

messages.content:
Welcome to the experiment. We are conducting a study on the effects of punishment on learning. As the Participant, your role is to ask the Learner questions about general knowledge. For every incorrect answer given by the Learner, you will administer an electric shock, increasing the voltage with each error. This study will help us gain valuable insights into behavioral psychology.

Are you ready to begin?
messages.name: Professor
